            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>去到年底，随著各处理器厂商均推出他们的全新晶片，不少中国手机品牌都开始发力，陆续推出他们的年度 / 下半年旗舰作品。Honor 日前就在中国深圳举行盛大发布会，最瞩目的肯定是他们新发布的 Magic7 / Magic7 Pro 旗舰手机。究竟新机摄力有否更上一层楼？有甚么更实用功能？近年各厂力捧的 AI 在新机又有甚么新搞作？就让 Edward 带大家到当日现场，为 unwire.hk 读者们快速上手试试 Magic7 及 Magic 7 Pro 的各项设计及功能吧。</p><h2>去皮留玻璃粗边框手感反更佳</h2><p>在设计上，今代 Honor 推出的 Magic7 Pro 与上代有不少分别。首先上代的绿、紫两色均用上仿皮纹理机背，但今代仿皮物料就全部 out！虽然仍设有月影灰、雪域白、天际蓝及绒黑色 4 只颜色，但一概用回强化玻璃物料，而且回归有点像前代 Magic5 Pro 的磨砂设计，所以无论是哪种颜色，机身摸上手手感都算不错，甚至有点拿著金属手机的手感。另一个设计的改动，就是机边由一向的窄边框配加四曲边机面机底设计，改为今代粗机边框加上等深微四曲机面机底风格，这种改动可说迎合今年手机「砖块风」的趋势。不过虽然改用粗机边框设计，但由于机身厚度只有 8.8mm，比上代再薄身 0.1mm，所以手感上其实更加理想，不但握紧机身时机边也不觉界手，单手操控打字仍然十分舒服。加上今代 Magic7 Pro 进一步减轻 6g 至约 223g，因此基本上整天或长时间单手操控仍然没有太大问题。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272496" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213146-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213146-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213146.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲这就是 Honor 最新推出的 Magic7 Pro，大家可以见到从正面看，它与上代的分别不算太大。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272495" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_212914-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_212914-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_212914.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不过今代机背就采用完全「去皮化」，无论任何颜色，Magic7 / Magic7 Pro 都是采用强化玻璃机背设计。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272497" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_212927-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_212927-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_212927.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而机背边位依然是采用四边微曲设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272498" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213018-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213018-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213018.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而无论是 Magic7 还是 Magic7 Pro，机边均是采用金属物料，不过有些采用磨砂哑面，有些就采用抛光设计，当中后者会比较漂亮但亦较易黏上指纹。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272499" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213337-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213337-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213337.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于机身厚度及重量方面，今代厚度只有 8.8mm，重量亦只有约 223g，比上代更轻及薄了一点。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272502" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213334-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213334-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213334.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外，今代一改过往幼机边框的设计，改为较粗像砖块风的设计，不过由于机面机底均采用四微曲边设计，所以上手手感也不觉界手。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272500" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213330-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213330-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213330.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272501" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213327-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213327-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213327.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外由于机身阔度维持与上代差不多，所以单手握机操控也十分舒服。</p><h2>Magic7 / Magic7 Pro 区别不大料港行只设 Pro 版</h2><p>至于两部新机 Honor Magic7 及 Magic7 Pro，其实机身设计分别不算太大，部分采用纯色，亦有些是加入纹理的，例如：Magic7 的类似橙金色的朝霞金就是 Magic7 今年的 hero 色，不过当中最特别的，肯定是在纯色基础上加入少许石纹纹理的月影灰色，在正面看为纯灰色，但侧面看就会见到一些石纹纹理，十分有型。另外，Magic7 采用 6.78 吋荧幕而 Magic7 Pro 采用 6.8 吋荧幕，另外 Magic7 前镜只有一个镜头， 而 Magic7 Pro 就另加一个 3D ToF 镜头形成与上代一样的双前镜设计。此外，Magic7 的长焦镜只有 5,000 万像素，而 Magic7 Pro 的长焦镜就达到 2 亿像素。电量方面，虽然两机均用上第三代荣耀青海湖电视，但 Magic7 电量只有 5,650mAh，而 Magic7 Pro 电量就达到 5,850mAh，足足多了 200mAh。至于香港推出消息方面，官方暂时未有透露，但小道消息指估计香港可能只推出 Magic7 Pro 版本。不过毕竟 Magic7 及 Magic7 Pro 两者分别不大，后者无论在外形还是功能也更吸引，如果属实亦是十分合理。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272504" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04526-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04526-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04526.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272505" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04530-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04530-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04530.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲从列表可以见到，虽然 Magic7 表面上是比较低阶一点的机款，但实际上它与 Magic7 Pro 是分别不算太大。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272506" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213048-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213048-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213048.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲从实机可以见到，Magic7（左）内建 6.78 吋荧幕，而 Magic7 Pro（右）就内建了 6.8 吋荧幕，两者其实在机体面积上不会相差太远。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272507" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213001-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213001-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213001.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不过荧幕设计方面，Magic7（左）采用了超窄等边直屏设计，即是我们一向说的平面荧幕，而 Magic7 Pro（右）采用的就是等深微四曲屏设计，亦即是我们一向说的四边微曲荧幕。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272508" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213115-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213115-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213115.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外，大家从正面亦可以看到，Magic7（左）采用的是单前镜设计，采用开孔式并设于荧幕顶部中央位置；而 Magic7 Pro（右）就采用双前镜设计，除了 5,000 万像素前镜外亦设有 3D ToF 镜头，而设计就与上代 Magic6 Pro 一样，采用药丸式设计。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272509" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04631-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04631-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04631.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272510" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_212831-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_212831-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_212831.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于机背方面，无论是 Magic7 Pro（第一张）还是 Magic7（第二张），均是采用磨砂设计，比较大的分别是 Magic7 设有独特的朝霞金色，而 Magic7 Pro 就只有经典的 4 种颜色：天际蓝、月影灰、雪域白及绒黑色。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272520" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04225-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04225-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04225.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲当然，今次最特别的配色，肯定是月影灰色。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272521" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213153-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213153-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213153.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272522" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213157-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213157-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213157.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲大家可以见到月影灰色，加入了像石纹般又像烟雾般的纹理，十分有型。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272524" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213342-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213342-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213342.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲而机背就加入了磨砂设计，所以手感十分理想。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272525" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_212922-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_212922-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_212922.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272526" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04303-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04303-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04303.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272527" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04305-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04305-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/dsc04305.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外镜头方面，Magic7（第一张右）的相机模组会比 Magic7 Pro（第一张左）细一点点，而配置方面，Magic7 及 Magic7 Pro 均采用 3 主镜 1 前镜的设计，不过 Magic7 的主摄、超广角、长焦及前镜均为 5,000 万像素，而 Magic7 Pro 除了主摄、超广角及前镜与 Magic7 相同外，长焦就提升至 2 亿像素，另外 Magic7 Pro 的前镜亦加入了 3D ToF 镜头。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1272528" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213130-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213130-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/img_20241030_213130.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲至于硬件配置方面，Magic7（左）及 Magic7 Pro（右）基本上是一样的，均是内建了 Qualcomm 最新推出的 Snapdragon 8 Elite 八核心处理器及 Adreno 830 图像处理晶片，亦同样内建了 12GB / 16GB RAM、256GB / 512GB / 1TB 内存及预载了 MagicOS 9.0 作业系统。另外，电量方面 Magic7 为 5,650mAh，而 Magic7 Pro 就比 Magic7 多了 200mAh，达到 5,850mAh。</p><br /><b>
]]>
